error.message:
The virtual network integration operation for the function app failed due to invalid subnet.
      Possible Causes: Subnet: '/subscriptions/azure_subscription_id/resourceGroups/myjstest/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworks/virtualnetworkabc/subnets/mySubnet' associated with the monitor is already in use or is not delegated to Microsoft.Web/serverFarms.
      Recommended Action: Retry the operation with a new subnet or use a one which is not already peered with any function app. If the issue persists, please create an issue here :- https://aka.ms/AAgc4fy.
